Renders the type documentation if called as \fIrender_type(Module, Type, Docs, Config)\fR.

.PP
Equivalent to \fIrender_type(Module, Type, Arity, Docs, #{})\fR if called as \fIrender_type(Module, Type, Arity, Docs)\fR.


